description: As Nate Stone stuffs himself with holiday cheer, he's unaware that a little elf is watching through the window. Ryan Pitt has come over to Nate's place to deliver a big Christmas package Nate is sure to love. Nate tries to act innocent but Ryan knows Nate has been a naughty boy, and that deep down, Nate's holiday wish is for just a taste of Ryan's candy cane. Ryan delivers all of that and then some as he stuffs much more than just Nate's stocking, candy coating him with his gift and making sure Nate has a white Christmas one way or another.Enjoy!
title: Holiday Stuffing
